<H3>daemon@ATHENA.MIT.EDU (Wed Mar 23 18:27:47 1994
)</H3>
<PRE>
Date: Wed, 23 Mar 1994 16:22:15 -0600 (MDT)
From: Lynxian Theologies &lt;BRANDON@cc.usu.edu&gt;
To: coldstuff@MIT.EDU
X-Vms-To: COLDSTUFF

It is available at:

  ftp://lab_backup.lib.usu.edu/pub/brandon/cold_dark/coldmud-0.10.patch1

It isn't extremely huge, but fixes some crippling bugs.  Changes:

+ divide by zero bug fixed, now throws ~div (Zachary)

+ random(0) bug fixed, now throws ~range (Zachary)

+ Database load/save error fixed (would segfault before) (Crag)

+ VERSION_BUGFIX changed to 1

-------------------------------------------------------------------------


-Brandon (Lynx)
